nd with him went up all the servants of Pharaoh, the elders of his house, and all the elders of the land of Egypt,","year":-1689},{"id":"rec1es2ni2WQZssoM","ref":"Gen.50.8","text":"And all the house of Joseph, and his brethren, and his father’s house: only their little ones, and their flocks, and their herds, they left in the land of Goshen.","year":-1689}]}
